The paper discusses a method for dimensionality reduction and data representation, which is commonly studied in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI, cs.LG). The method is applied to natural language processing (cs.CL) and statistical analysis (cs.DS), and the paper presents numerical experiments to demonstrate its feasibility (cs.IR).
